title: Restructuring Flower One
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Kellen O'Keefe, CEO at Flower One joins Rena Sherbill to discuss his journey from MedMen, what he's learned along the way and what he's excited about in Nevada. Building valuable corporate governance. Management changes throughout the cannabis industry, moving from license acquirers and expanders to strategic operators. MSOs building their advantage through evolving legalization. Inter-state commerce still far off. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
